            <h3 class="post-title">
                Why wasn't I approved to adopt a dog?
            </h3>
            <p class="post-meta">
                Here in PAWSter Care we have sets of Policies and Protocols that we follow and if only one of those were not met you may not adopt a dog. We hope you won’t let this one experience change your mind about providing a loving home to a pet in need. Thank you for helping an adoptable pet and we wish you the best of luck in your search to find a new member of your family. 
                
            </p>
